ing: 2 (10.75 ounce) cans condensed cream of celery soup
des: "A very tasty and easy slow cooker pork tenderloin using cream of celery that goes well over rice."
ins:
Season pork tenderloin with pepper, and place in slow cooker. Pour undiluted celery soup onto tenderloin, covering meat completely.
Cover, and cook on Low for 8 hours.
